Entries.default: "Easier when you poison them first, right?"
"I don't know that this place agreed with our fungal friend - anymore than it does with me."
"Seems like nothing lives here for long. Best it can do is survive a while."
"Perhaps they did not adapt to this cage as well as I thought."
"The state that thing was in, you probably could've offed it with a well-placed kick."
"What if we ate it? Would we die, too?"
"It was in agony. Yet I wouldn't say we offered mercy."
"Belfetto, it's done. And there's no lingering doubt to torment us later."
"That is Eora's law. Die or do not."
